Program: The Forum
Title: Are we Losing the Ability to Focus?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p032k6qz
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 23 Sep 2015
In the age of perpetual distraction, are we losing the ability to focus? Bridget Kendall is joined by three guests who have found a way to concentrate. David Hieatt is a Welsh denim jeans entrepreneur, his personal and professional maxim is “do one thing well”. Slovenian violinist Miha Pogacnik uses music to empower business leaders and Icelandic lawyer Ragnar Jonasson is also a writer, his latest novel “Snow Blind” is a mystery set in a remote fishing village. Photo: A watchmaker examines a watch mechanism (Photo Credit: Getty Images) Show less